               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of Divinity, ሠይፈ፡ መለኮት፡; Asmat Prayers for the Days of the Week</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="13r" facs="003">Fols 1r–13r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2295Sayfam">Sayfa malakot</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="13r" to="15r" facs="015">Fols 13r–15r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against epilepsy and Legewon, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ባሪያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡</foreign></title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ባሪያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ላሐቅሬጅ፡ ነቅ፡ መግኑን፡ ወልቅሶን፡ በስሶን፡ ነበለሶመን፡ ዘነበቦሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="15r" to="18r" facs="017">Fols 15r–18r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for drowning [demons], <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስጥመ፡</foreign></title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">A‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መሥጥም፡ ዘእለተ፡ ሰኑይ፡ ‎‎ዓቃቢሁኒ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ መላ[እክ]ት፡ ጅዘክሙ፡ ላሕ፡ ጅዘክሙላህ፡ ‎‎ጅዘክሙ፡ ላህ፡ እንሰሪፉ፡ እስሪፉ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="18v" to="26v" facs="021">Fols 18v–26v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Another Asmat prayer against epilepsy and Legewon, arranged for Tuesday</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>‎ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ መውሥምት፡ ፌራ፡ ወንዳድ፡ ‎‎ምችወምታት፡ አጋንንት፡ ፀዋጋን፡ ወሠይጣናት፡ ርጉማን፡ ወመናፍስት፡ ‎‎ርኩሳን፡ ወሰብእ፡ መሠርያን፡ ወልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡ እኩያን፡ ወኩሎሙ፡ ‎‎ሠራዊተ፡ ዲያብሎስ፡‎<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="27r" to="32r" facs="029">Fols 27r–32r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Another Asmat prayer against epilepsy and Legewon, arranged for Wednesday</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎በስመ፡ እብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ በእንተ[፡] ሕማመ[፡] ባርያ[፡] ‎‎ወሌጌዎን፡ አጋንንት፡ ወሰይጣናት፡ ወመናፍስት፡ ርኩሳን፡ ወሰብእ፡ ‎‎መሠርያን መጋኛ[፡]ወጉሥምት፡ ፍልፀት፡ ወቁርፀት፡<gap reason="omitted"/> መሥጥም[፡] ‎‎ዘእለተ፡ ረቡዕ፡ አቃ[ቢ]ሁኒ፡ ዑራኤል፡ መላክ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <locus from="32r" to="36r" facs="034">Fols 32r–36r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Another Asmat prayer against epilepsy and Legewon, arranged for Thursday</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎በእንተ፡ ባሪያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ አጋንንት፡ ወሰይጣናት፡ ወመናፍስት፡ ርኩሳን፡‎‎<gap reason="omitted"/> መስጥም[፡] በእለተ፡ ሐሙስ፡ አቃቢሁኒ፡ ራጉኤል፡ መላክ፡‎ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     <locus from="36v" to="39r" facs="039">Fols 36v–39r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Another Asmat prayer against epilepsy and Legewon, arranged for Friday</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ[፡] ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ አጋንንት፡ ፀዋጋን፡ ‎‎ወሰይጣናት፡ ርጉማን፡‎ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎መሥጥም[፡]ዘእለተ፡ ዓርብ፡ አቃቢኒ፡ አፍኒን፡ መላክ፡ ሊቀ[፡] መላእክት፡ ‎‎አልዝትራእርካህ፡ ክናንህ፡‎ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                     <locus from="39r" to="41v" facs="041">Fols 39r–41v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Another Asmat prayer against epilepsy and Legewon, arranged for Saturday</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ወልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወአልጉም፡ ‎‎ወረገን፡ ጅን፡ ወደባስ፡ ወኩሎሙ፡ ሠራዊተ፡ ዲያብሎስ፡ ወሠራዊተ፡ ‎‎ቡዳ። ወአባለ፡ ንጉሥ። መሥጥም፡ ዘእለተ፡ ቀዳሚት፡ ሰንበት፡ ዓቃቢሁኒ፡ ‎‎ራጉኤል፡ መላክ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡‎ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                     <locus from="41v" to="47v" facs="044">Fols 41v–47v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Another Asmat prayer against epilepsy and Legewon, arranged for Sunday</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ[፡] ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ[፡] ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ አጋንንት፡ ወሠይጣናት፡ ‎‎ወመናፍስት፡ ርኩሳን፡ ወሰብእ፡ መሠርያን፡ መሥጥም፡ ዘእለተ፡ ዕሁድ፡ ‎‎ሰንበት፡ ዓቃቢሁኒ፡ ሳቁ[ኤ]ል፡ መላክ፡ ሊቀ[፡]መላእክት፡ ኮክ፥ቡኒ፡ ‎‎ሻምሻ፡ አላሁ‎፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
